      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has clearly been well-maintained over the years. The exterior paint still has a beautiful shine, though upon close inspection, you'll find some minor stone chips on the front bumper and a few faint surface scratches. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free, with only light wear on the driver's seat bolster. It runs smoothly and all features are fully functional, making it a reliable choice for its next owner.",
