      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I\u2019m looking to find a new home for this absolute gem! It\u2019s been such a reliable ride and still drives like a dream. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has plenty of life left in it\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable car without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and I\u2019d love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm happy to chat!",
