    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E92 M3, featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 and a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox. This example delivers a visceral 8,400 RPM redline and has been proactively maintained with rod bearing and throttle actuator replacements. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC) for adjustable damping rates and an M Variable Differential Lock for precise corner-exit traction. While showing minor signs of use, the powertrain remains exceptionally tight, providing the linear torque curve and induction symphony enthusiasts crave.",
